oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Old Timers Quartet - 1949-06-11
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM program featuring the Old Timers Quartet (also styled as Old-Timers' Quartet and Ol' Timers' Quartet), originally broadcast 1949-06-11. Personnel include David Cobb (announcer), Frank Marlowe (host), and Joseph MacPherson (performer).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Old Timers Quartet; Joseph MacPherson
